{"title": "Y1234", "summary": "Modular Profile Luminaire", "body": "A minimal tapered aluminium profile that provides a wide spread of light. This versatile module can be assembled in different configurations to form a downlight, uplight or an array of light.\n\n*2020*\n\n[lp=Y2-Production.jpg]\n\n{[sp=Y1234 - P981.jpg]     [sp=Y1234 - P982.jpg]}\n{[sp=Y1234 - P983.jpg][sp=Y1234 - P984.jpg]}\n[lp=Y1234 - P984 Main.jpg]\n\n\n**&&Sketches & Prototypes&&**\n\n\n[lp=Y1234 Sketch.jpg]\n\n[lp=Y1234-Prototype.jpg]\n\n\n**&&Vertical Variant&&**\n\n\n[lp=P994-SCENE.jpg]\n\n\n**&&Acoustic Felt Variant&&**\n\n\n[lp=P980-Scene.jpg]\n[sp=P980 - Aster(PETAL).jpg][sp=P980 - Aster(OVAL).jpg][sp=P980 - Aster(TRAPEZE).jpg]\n\nTo save space, the acoustic panels are shipped flat. The magnetic top cap is easily removed to reveal notches in which the panels are inserted and fastened with screws. Place the cap back.\n\n[lp=P980-INSTALLATION SITE.jpg]\n\n{[sp=Aster CAP ON.jpg][sp=Aster CAP OFF.jpg]}", "image": "Y1234 - P982 Cover.jpg", "id": 18}